metadata.name: Fancy Honey Jar #1
metadata.description: This is the NFT of Fancy Honey Jar from Fancy Bears Metaverse. It plays a key role in Phase II and Phase III of the FBM $HONEY system. It also holds $HONEY tokens. All $HONEY jars were claimed in February and March 2022 and each one of them initially held 71000 $HONEY tokens.
